  "payload": {
    "lesson": {
      "language": "zh-CN",
      "meta": "交互解题 · 线面角",
      "title": "正方体ABCD-A₁B₁C₁D₁中，棱长为1，求直线A₁C与底面ABCD所成角的正弦值",
      "answerLabel": "直线 A₁C 与底面 ABCD 所成角的正弦值",
      "answerValue": "$\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$"
    },
    "steps": [
      {
        "title": "建立空间直角坐标系",
        "content": "<p>以顶点 $A$ 为原点，$AB$、$AD$、$AA_1$ 分别为 $x$、$y$、$z$ 轴建立坐标系。</p><p>因为棱长为 $1$，关键点坐标为：</p>$$A(0, 0, 0), C(1, 1, 0), A_1(0, 0, 1)$$",
        "highlight": [
          "Axis"
        ],
        "cameraPos": {
          "x": 6,
          "y": 5,
          "z": 7
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "求直线 A₁C 的方向向量",
        "content": "<p>直线 $A_1C$ 的方向向量为：</p>$$\\vec{A_1C} = C - A_1 = (1, 1, -1)$$",
        "highlight": [
          "Line_A1C"
        ],
        "cameraPos": {
          "x": 5,
          "y": 4,
          "z": 8
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "确定底面 ABCD 的法向量",
        "content": "<p>底面 $ABCD$ 在平面 $z = 0$ 上，其法向量竖直向上：</p>$$\\vec{n} = (0, 0, 1)$$",
        "highlight": [
          "Line_A1C",
          "Plane_ABCD",
          "Normal_Vector"
        ],
        "cameraPos": {
          "x": 4,
          "y": 6,
          "z": 5
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "利用向量公式求解",
        "content": "<p>设直线 $A_1C$ 与底面所成角为 $\\theta$。</p><p>线面角公式：$\\sin\\theta = \\dfrac{|\\vec{A_1C} \\cdot \\vec{n}|}{|\\vec{A_1C}|\\,|\\vec{n}|}$</p><p>计算数量积与模长：</p>$$\\vec{A_1C} \\cdot \\vec{n} = -1, \\quad |\\vec{A_1C}| = \\sqrt{3}$$<p>代入公式：</p>$$\\sin\\theta = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$$<p>所以，直线 $A_1C$ 与底面 $ABCD$ 所成角的正弦值为 $\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$。</p>",
        "highlight": [
          "Line_A1C",
          "Plane_ABCD",
          "Normal_Vector"
        ],
        "cameraPos": {
          "x": 5,
          "y": 5,
          "z": 6
        }
      }
    ],
